mark iv <iv> starts bid for conrac <cax>
    new york, march 24 - 
mark iv industries inc said it has started the 25 dlr per share tender
offer for all shares of conrac corp that it announced yesterday
afternoon. in a newspaper advertisement, the company said the offer
and withdrawal rights expire april 20 unless extended. the offer is
not conditioned on receipt of any minimum number of shares but is
conditioned on the arrangement of financing. mark iv already owns
about 9.9 pct of conrac's 6.8 mln shares outstanding. reuter 
